description: Welcome Home to 330 Dorchester St! Step into the spacious open concept living area, flooded with natural light, featuring hardwood floors throughout. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting top-of-the-line Jenn-Air appliances, pristine quartz countertops, and ample storage space. This 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom unit offers a timeless design. The x-large primary suite provides a spa like feel with its en-suite bathroom and walk in closet. A second bedroom offers versatility for guests or a home office, while a second full bathroom offers comfort for guests! This unit is in the middle of it all and just across from many of Boston's most anticipated development projects, including Washington Village, a new community already in the works. Washington village plans on bringing new life to the Andrew Square neighborhood including 746 residential units, more than 82,000 square feet of retail space, and will be adding much needed open green space to the area.
